features: COMPLETE PACKAGE: Select your preferred color. Our Two-Pocket Folders are expertly crafted from sturdy, heavyweight paper with a matte finish, specifically designed to hold Letter Sheet Size (8 1/2" x 11") documents.
SPACIOUS POCKETS: Each folder features deep pockets, with a generous 4" capacity, capable of securely holding up to 50 letter-size sheets. Say goodbye to worries about overflowing pockets.

PROFESSIONAL QUALITY: Our folders are equipped with 2 four-corner business card holders to prevent cards from popping out. We use high-quality paper material and inks, ensuring increased durability and vibrant color consistency.

VERSATILE USAGE: Ideal for business, school, or home use. Perfect for professional presentations, brochure handouts, training materials, and conference meeting guides. Also, an essential addition to any student or teacher's back-to-school supplies list, as well as for keeping your home organized.

USER-FRIENDLY DESIGN: Our innovative two-pocket design uses continuous material without glue in the center fold. This ensures hassle-free insertion of papers without binding, while still allowing for maximum load size. These folders are both flexible and durable, perfect for your organizational needs.
